No `dependencies` (fictional, no third-party libs). Version matches workspace convention.

### 7. `extensions/pulseboard/openclaw.plugin.json`

```json
{
  "id": "pulseboard",
  "channels": ["pulseboard"],
  "configSchema": {
    "type": "object",
    "additionalProperties": false,
